{"tid":558554,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"NETFLIX原創劇碳變討論區，有錢人無限換身體，永恆不死","createTime":"2018-02-12T11:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T07:44:26.000Z","uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f0328ba0e9a63f292241156b96849bc74b235021","tid":558554,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:20:25.000Z","msg":"最近追開呢套<br />\n<br />\n第一集就幾多囡囡露波波<br />\n<br />\n真係好吸引<br />\n<br />\n有錢人無限換身體，永恆不死，窮 人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲同我一樣追緊呢套？"},{"pid":"fe90e219244c31fd5e2af09b2c818495b37be5ce","tid":558554,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:20:58.000Z","msg":"碳變》（英語：Altered Carbon）是一部於Netflix播出的美國科幻影集，改編自英國作家理查&middot;K&middot;摩根的2002年同名小說《碳變》；該劇由萊塔&middot;卡羅格里迪斯負責擔任節目統籌[1][2]。第一季共10集，並於2018年2月2日首播[3]。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劇情[編輯]<br />\n故事背景設定於當今三百年後的未來世界。此時，人類心智不僅能夠數位化，還能在人體之間互相下載、傳送。某日，受過專業訓練的軍團士兵武&middot;科瓦奇在重生後，他受命前去調查富翁羅倫斯&middot;班克勞遭人謀殺的案件。在調查過程中，科瓦奇開始意識到自己的過去並不單純。"},{"pid":"8bb0d6eee44553d5b038084b6713d7e4e19c98c2","tid":558554,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://zeekmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1515857358-3626850d481efd38a8ae8164011f41b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzeekmagazine.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2F1515857358-3626850d481efd38a8ae8164011f41b2.jpg&h=6c6c794b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正"},{"pid":"25a5ede9a35a56da022922fd5895a13565f0fabd","tid":558554,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T11:22:53.000Z","msg":"不過唔明點解會搵日本仔？泡菜仔？做主角<br />\n<br />\n上左英國鬼身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f82c4b03a10d0897bf49f144bba4532b97d7e3c3","tid":558554,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T13:10:48.000Z","msg":"想買不死鳥風褸，點買先最抵？<br />\